            "notes": "The deck focuses on controlling the game through counterspells, removal, and card advantage. It includes a variety of interaction spells such as Counterspell, Cryptic Command, and Force of Negation to disrupt opponents' strategies. The deck also features removal spells like Fatal Push, Swords to Plowshares, and Toxic Deluge to deal with threats efficiently. Card advantage is generated through cards like Brainstorm, Demonic Tutor, and Snapcaster Mage. The mana base is optimized with fetch lands, dual lands, and utility lands to ensure consistent mana production. The goal of the deck is to control the board, disrupt opponents' plans, and outvalue them with card advantage to secure victory in a 1 vs 1 format."
